About Michigan Legacy Art Park

Michigan Legacy Art Park is non-profit contemporary sculpture park located on two miles of hiking trails amidst a 30-acre hardwood forest preserve in Benzie County, Michigan.

The organization's mission is to inspire awareness, appreciation and passion for Michiganâ€™s history, culture and environment through the arts.
